import React from 'react' 
import './Content.css'
import { Switch, Route} from 'react-router-dom'
import About from '../../views/exemples/About'
const Content = props => (
<main className="Content">
<Switch>
    <Route path="/about">
<About />
    </Route>
</Switch>
</main>
)

export default Content
